T1  - Heterogeneity in bank valuation of LDC debt: Evidence from the 1988 Brazilian debt-reduction program
AU  - Demirgüç-Kunt, Ash
AU  - Diwan, Ishac
AU  - Spiegel, Mark M.
JO  - Journal of Monetary Economics
VL  - 39
IS  - 3
